text: Nima Ebrahimnejad (, born 21 February 1969) is an Iranian former cyclist. He competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Iranian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Iran Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
